{"tid":1467492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我認頭先有屌前線 我say sorry  不割","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:09.000Z","uid":217275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07625329e4fdfb6d5cff18a5a9f5efb2b55e233e","tid":1467492,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"我認睇live睇到燥 , 但我希望前線亦都要思考煽動問題 因為勇武嗰班真係好容易比人煽動 不論有鬼定真心都好容易群上,  慢慢變成帶風向... 希望前線手足多啲逆向思維諗一諗"},{"pid":"395cda96f079236e53b53b8b933b6e720e4225e7","tid":1467492,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4389ad8764f33410edce33a072c354b19fb95b4c","tid":1467492,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7381c01439ab00b30e8aac8ef60e7cae2df917d5","tid":1467492,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須保護100%和理非行動 <br />\n<br />\n我地可以提早決定100%和理非定 有後續 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察風向 破壞連登 咩淪陷 唔好信<br />\n<br />\n信左就中警察計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議民陣遊行必須 100%和理非 否則就當卧底</span>"},{"pid":"c3d5fc295e042c33d6bf77fa67354b2d833619d4","tid":1467492,"uid":280149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化 不割蓆 <br />\n和而不同 屌完就改進 我愛大家"}]}